sa has been stolen, which led to an adventure to try and retrieve it.\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1995, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1919, \"end\": 1928, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Lisa\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.204426544820582e-31, \"text\": \"Mona Lisa\", \"types\": [\"Q386724\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Lisa\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Mona_Lisa\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The masked figure\", \"from\": 1875, \"to\": 1892}, {\"ngram\": \"an adventure\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1971}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The journey included galloping across the Seine on a glimmering horse and eventually delivering the Olympic flag.\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2109, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2038, \"end\": 2043, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 6.180064000019117e-32, \"text\": \"Seine\", \"types\": [\"Q47521\", \"Q4022\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Seine\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The journey\", \"from\": 1996, \"to\": 2007}, {\"ngram\": \"a glimmering horse\", \"from\": 2047, \"to\": 2065}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic flag\", \"from\": 2092, \"to\": 2108}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Related Concurrent with the flotilla of athletes was a series of musical performances, starting with superstarLady Gaga,who performed a rendition of\\u00c2 Zizi Jeanmaire\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMon Truc en Plumes,\\\" or \\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cMy Thing With Feathers.\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009d Flanked by a group of backup dancers dressed in all black and carrying pink feather fans, a similarly befeathered Gaga sang and danced at the foot of the Seine.\", \"from\": 2111, \"to\": 2498, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2227, \"end\": 2231, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Lady_Gaga\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 3.0618425983541222e-56, \"text\": \"Gaga\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wi