3}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Following her performance, she took toher Instagramto share her thoughts.\\u00c2 \\\"I feel so completely grateful to have been asked to open the Paris@Olympics2024 this year.\", \"from\": 2499, \"to\": 2666, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her performance\", \"from\": 2509, \"to\": 2524}, {\"ngram\": \"toher\", \"from\": 2535, \"to\": 2540}, {\"ngram\": \"Instagramto\", \"from\": 2541, \"to\": 2552}, {\"ngram\": \"her thoughts\", \"from\": 2559, \"to\": 2571}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris@Olympics2024\", \"from\": 2632, \"to\": 2654}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am also humbled to be asked by the Olympics organizing committee to sing such a special French song\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094a song to honor the French people and their tremendous history of art, music, and theatre,\\\" the singer wrote.\", \"from\": 2667, \"to\": 2880, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2757, \"end\": 2763, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 0.669865048129449, \"rank\": 0.2608319394035794, \"text\": \"French\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}, {\"begin\": 2791, \"end\": 2804, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"French people\", \"types\": [\"Q41710\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/French_people\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the Olympics organizing committee\", \"from\": 2700, \"to\": 2733}, {\"ngram\": \"their tremendous history\", \"from\": 2809, \"to\": 2833}, {\"ngram\": \"art\", \"from\": 2837, \"to\": 2840}, {\"ngram\": \"music\", \"from\": 2842, \"to\": 2847}, {\"ngram\": \"theatre\", \"from\": 2853, \"to\": 2860}, {\"ngram\": \"the singer\", \"from\": 2863, \"to\": 2873}]}, {\"sentence\": \"\\\"Although I am not a French artist, I have always felt a very special connection with Fre