ing for,\\u00c2Celine Dion's first public performance since halting her tour amid her struggles with Stiff Person Syndrome (SPS).\", \"from\": 6285, \"to\": 6573, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6568, \"end\": 6571, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"score\": 0.888143547249822, \"rank\": 0.12356669947715498, \"text\": \"SPS\", \"types\": [\"Q7278\", \"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Socialist_Party_of_Serbia\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"his country\", \"from\": 6295, \"to\": 6306}, {\"ngram\": \"a gold medal\", \"from\": 6307, \"to\": 6319}, {\"ngram\": \"the team\", \"from\": 6340, \"to\": 6348}, {\"ngram\": \"pursuit cycling event\", \"from\": 6349, \"to\": 6370}, {\"ngram\": \"London\", \"from\": 6374, \"to\": 6380}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6381, \"to\": 6382}, {\"ngram\": \"The evening\", \"from\": 6383, \"to\": 6394}, {\"ngram\": \"the moment\", \"from\": 6411, \"to\": 6421}, {\"ngram\": \"so many fans\", \"from\": 6422, \"to\": 6434}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2Celine Dion's first public performance\", \"from\": 6457, \"to\": 6496}, {\"ngram\": \"her tour\", \"from\": 6511, \"to\": 6519}, {\"ngram\": \"her struggles\", \"from\": 6525, \"to\": 6538}, {\"ngram\": \"Stiff Person Syndrome\", \"from\": 6544, \"to\": 6565}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Dion was first diagnosed with the rare and progressive neurological disorder in 2022 and has battled a litany of physical symptoms that have inhibited powerhouse vocal abilities from operating as usual.\", \"from\": 6574, \"to\": 6776, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 6574, \"to\": 6578}, {\"ngram\": \"the rare and progressive neurological disorder\", \"from\": 6604, \"to\": 6650}, {\"ngram\": \"a litany\", \"from\": 6675, \"to\": 6683}, {\"ngram\": \"physical symptoms\", \"from\": 6687, \"to\": 6704}, {\"ngram\": \"powerhouse vocal abilities\", \"from\": 6725, \"to\": 6751}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In June, Dion appeared before a New York audience at a screening of\\\"I Am: Celine Dion,\\\"an intimate documentary that revealed the depth of her health plight.\\u00c2 This was the second time the French-Canadian singer had headlined at the Olympic opening ceremony.\", \"from\": 6777, \"to\": 7034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 6809, \"end\": 6817, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"score\": 0.9999999999399733, \"rank\": 5.97178680855181e-11, \"text\": \"New York\", \"types\": [\"Q515\", \"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/New_York_City\"}, {\"begin\": 6851, \"end\": 6862, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 5.206562943884752e-77, \"text\": \"Celine Dion\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Celine_Dion\"}, {\"begin\": 6965, \"end\": 6980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.6821036797354377, \"rank\": 0.44930733234641995, \"text\": \"French-Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}, {\"begin\": 6965, \"end\": 6980, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"score\": 0.6821036797354377, \"rank\": 0.44930733234641995, \"text\": \"French-Canadian\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Canada\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"June\", \"from\": 6780, \"to\": 6784}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 6786, \"to\": 6790}, {\"ngram\": \"a screening of\\\"I Am\", \"from\": 6830, \"to\": 6849}, {\"ngram\": \"the depth\", \"from\": 6902, \"to\": 6911}, {\"ngram\": \"her health plight\", \"from\": 6915, \"to\": 6932}, {\"ngram\": \"\\u00c2\", \"from\": 6933, \"to\": 6934}, {\"ngram\": \"the second time\", \"from\": 6944, \"to\": 6959}, {\"ngram\": \"the Olympic opening ceremony\", \"from\": 7004, \"to\": 7032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Nearly 20 years ago, Dion sang her song,\\\"The Power of the Dream,\\\"at the 1996 Summer Games.\", \"from\": 7035, \"to\": 7125, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 7056, \"to\": 7060}, {\"ngram\": \"song,\\\"The Power\", \"from\": 7070, \"to\": 7085}, {\"ngram\": \"the 1996 Summer Games\", \"from\": 7103, \"to\": 7124}]}, {\"sentence\": \"From the platform midway up the iconic Eiffel Tower, Dion \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 wearing a diamond-encrusted gown with glittering fringe \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 exuded strength and resilience as she belted out Edith Piaf's\\u00c2 \\\"Hymne \\u00c3 l\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099amour,\\\" or \\\"Hymn to Love.\\\"\", \"from\": 7127, \"to\": 7352, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7298, \"end\": 7308, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"score\": 0.9999999912251951, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Edith Piaf\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q483501\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/\\u00c9dith_Piaf\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the platform\", \"from\": 7132, \"to\": 7144}, {\"ngram\": \"midway\", \"from\": 7145, \"to\": 7151}, {\"ngram\": \"the iconic Eiffel Tower\", \"from\": 7155, \"to\": 7178}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 7180, \"to\": 7188}, {\"ngram\": \"a diamond-encrusted gown\", \"from\": 7197, \"to\": 7221}, {\"ngram\": \"glittering fringe \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\", \"from\": 7227, \"to\": 7248}, {\"ngram\": \"strength\", \"from\": 7256, \"to\": 7264}, {\"ngram\": \"resilience\", \"from\": 7269, \"to\": 7279}, {\"ngram\": \"Hymne \\u00c3\", \"from\": 7313, \"to\": 7320}, {\"ngram\": \"\\\"Hymn\", \"from\": 7336, \"to\": 7341}, {\"ngram\": \"Love\", \"from\": 7345, \"to\": 7349}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Arms outstretched to Olympians and her fans alike, Dion at several points during the song appeared to become emotional.\", \"from\": 7353, \"to\": 7472, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Arms\", \"from\": 7353, \"to\": 7357}, {\"ngram\": \"Olympians\", \"from\": 7374, \"to\": 7383}, {\"ngram\": \"her fans\", \"from\": 7388, \"to\": 7396}, {\"ngram\": \"Dion\", \"from\": 7404, \"to\": 7408}, {\"ngram\": \"several points\", \"from\": 7412, \"to\": 7426}, {\"ngram\": \"the song\", \"from\": 7434, \"to\": 7442}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She never faltered, however, and as her voice soared in the night, the Eiffel Tower \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00c2 embossed with the five interlaced Olympic rings \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00c2 glittered in the background.\", \"from\": 7473, \"to\": 7643, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her voice\", \"from\": 7509, \"to\": 7518}, {\"ngram\": \"the night\", \"from\": 7529, \"to\": 7538}, {\"ngram\": \"the five interlaced Olympic rings \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094\\u00c2\", \"from\": 7576, \"to\": 7614}, {\"ngram\": \"the background\", \"from\": 7628, \"to\": 7642}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Immediately following Dion's performance, singer Kelly Clarkson \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 who, along with former NFL player Peyton Manning and sports commentator Mike Tirico served as NBC's broadcast team for the ceremony \\u00e2\\u0080\\u0094 was emotionally overwhelmed.\\u00c2\\u00e2\\u0080\\u009cPeople don\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099t know her story, what she\\u00e2\\u0080\\u0099s been going through physically,\\\" Clarkson eventually said.\", \"from\": 7645, \"to\": 7982, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 7694, \"end\": 7708, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Kelly Clarkson\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Kelly_Clarkson\"}, {\"begin\"